              <h4>1800 Seat Multi-purpose Room &#45;Crown Ridge &#40;2008&#41;</h4>
              <p>The challenge on this project was that because the room was multi-propose the acoustics were far from ideal. However, with careful design, computer modeling, and the Nexo 1230 speakers Clarity Media Group was able to design a system that resulted in a +/-1db sound level throughout the space.</p>
              <h4>Equipment Installed</h4>
