              </ul>
              <h4>500 Seat Uniform SPL &#45;North Central Campus &#40;2010&#41;</h4>
              <p>The challenge on this project was similar to the challenge with the multi-purpose room - how to get as uniform SPL as possible.</p>
              <h4>Equipment Installed</h4>
