                <li><a href="http://www.aviom.com/AviomProducts/A-16II-Personal-Mixer.php" target="_blank">&#40;1&#41; Aviom Personal Monitor System</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://jands.com/vista/vista-m1-control-surface/" target="_blank">&#40;1&#41; Lighting System&#45;a Jands Vista M1 was used to control all the optipars and LED lighting fixtures</a></li>
