              <h4>200 Seat Space&#45; Crown Ridge Auxilary Room &#40;2010&#41;</h4>
              <p>The challenge was to come up with a sound system appropriate to a small space. Previously the room just had some speakers mounted on a pole. The new equipment speakers are <a href="http://www.toaelectronics.com/spk0027.asp" target="_blank">Toa HX-5.</a></p>
