              <p>Absolutely&#33; One of the strengths of Clarity Media Group is our long history of mentoring church sound technicians including volunteers. Over the years we have developed a clear understanding of what is reasonable to expect a volunteer to be able to master. With the advent of digital consoles, you can have a standard setup saved so even if everything gets messed up you can always reset it back to a known condition.</p>
