                <li>The monitor speaker system is a combination of Yamaha IF-2108 and IF-2208</li>
                <li>Using the new MyMix monitoring system, musicians are able to record the practice on a standard SD card and take it home to rehearse the songs palying along with the other instruments.</li>
                <li>A single piece of Cat5 cable controls 56 input channels and 32 output channels.</li>
                <li>To provide superior micing of the choir, Audix M1255B high gain choir mics were suspended from the ceiling.</li>
                <li>To blend in with the background, all the speakers were custom ordered in white.</li>
